      "content": "<bpt id=\"p8\">**</bpt>Spark<ept id=\"p8\">**</ept><ph id=\"ph6\"/> - Apache Spark is an open-source parallel processing framework that supports in-memory processing to boost the performance of big-data analytic applications. Spark's in-memory computation capabilities make it a good choice for iterative algorithms in machine learning and graph computations.",
